  "title": "Marketing and Sales Executive",
  "description": "<h3>🌟 What You’ll Do:</h3><ul><li>Contribute to marketing and sales initiatives</li><li>Follow up with new customers</li><li>Create consultancy deliverables: reports, presentations, training materials</li><li>Assist in HR and business consultancy projects</li><li>Help organize and deliver client training programs</li><li>Translate documents between English and Chinese</li><li>Communicate effectively with internal and external stakeholders</li><li>You are required to work after office hours sometimes</li></ul><p>✅ What We’re Looking For:</p><ul><li>Strong communication skills</li><li>Able to communicate with English-speaking and Chinese-speaking customers</li><li>Willingness to meet customers</li></ul><p>🎁 What You’ll Get:</p><ul><li>Broad exposure to multiple industries and clients</li><li>Competitive base salary + profit-sharing scheme</li><li>A collaborative, growth-focused work environment</li></ul><h3>📬 Ready to Apply?</h3><p><strong>Contact:</strong> Jerry Li 📧 Email: jerry@cadencehrconsulting.com 📱 WhatsApp: +65 93891616</p>",
